      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like everyone is trying to force me to stay in a house that's on fire. they're so focused on \"finding a way forward\" that they don't realize the only way out is through the exit. there is a certain kind of mercy in just letting go, isn't there? to just stop the cycle of suffering once and for all. it feels like the only way to actually be compassionate to myself is to stop the pain entirely.",
